<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row mt-5 mb-5">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <h1>Sign up for a free evaluation</h1>
            <p>At Flight, we don't believe in a one size fits all fitness program. Every person's fitness goals and ability is different. Whether you are a seasoned athlete or completely new to working out, we want to be able to serve your needs best. This is why we recommend anyone interested in training at Flight to come in for a free evaluation. This gives us an opportunity to get to know you and your fitness goals so that we can tailor a program to your needs.</p>

            <hr class="mt-3 mb-3" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <%= form_with url: evaluation_path, id: 'register-form' do |f|%>
        <div class="row mb-2 mt-2">
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                <label>Name: </label>
                <%= f.text_field "name", class: "form-control form-control-lg", required: true %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                <label>Email: </label>
                <%= f.email_field "email", class: "form-control form-control-lg", required: true %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-2 mb-2">
            <div class="col">
                <label>Fitness Goals</label>
                <%= f.text_area "goals", class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-2 mb-2">
            <div class="col">
                <label>Previous Training Experience</label>
                <%= f.text_area "experience", class: "form-control" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-2 mb-2">
            <div class="col">
                <label>Past Injury History</label>
                <%= f.text_area "injury_history", class: "form-control" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-2 mt-2">
            <div class="col-12 mt-2 mb-2">
                <h5>Availability</h5>
            </div>
            <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <label>Time <%= i %>: </label>
                    <%= f.text_field "[times][#{i}]", class: "form-control form-control-lg datetimepicker-input", data: {toggle: "datetimepicker", target:"#datetimepicker#{i}"}, id: "datetimepicker#{i}", required: true %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-3 mb-3">
            <div class="col">
                <%= f.submit "Sign up", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% end %>
</div>
